{"article_id":"LflgDva6MaEsEXAi","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"As technical problems with the government 's new health insurance marketplace slow the pace of sign-up ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"a variety of `` fixes '' have been proposed .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"But some of these would create their own challenges .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"In rough order from least to most disruptive , here are some of the ideas :","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"This is everyone 's favorite idea .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"The Obama administration says","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"it hopes to have HealthCare.gov working smoothly for most users by the end of November ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"though it 's not clear that target will be met .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"A 1-800 number and enrollment by mail can save would-be customers hours in front of a frozen computer screen .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"But ultimately , all the enrollments have to be processed through the same computer system .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Customers can use HealthCare.gov or commercial websites","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"to shop for coverage","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"without a lengthy enrollment process ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"then contact insurers directly","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"to sign up for coverage .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"For now at least , though , people","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"who use this option","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"will not be able to take advantage of government subsidies .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"If timely enrollment is not possible ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"there will be pressure","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"to extend various deadlines , beyond mid-December for coverage","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"that begins in January","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"and beyond late March","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"to avoid a penalty .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"Without the pressure of these deadlines , though ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"younger , healthier people may wait longer","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"to sign up ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"leaving a sicker , costlier pool of patients covered","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"and potentially driving up premiums .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Lawmakers are considering options","depth":4},{"id":30,"text":"to codify the president 's promise","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"that people","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"who like their old health insurance","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"can keep it ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"even if those plans do n't meet the minimum standards","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"set by the Affordable Care Act","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"and are n't already grandfathered in .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Experts cite several potential problems with that :","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"Those policies do n't include the consumer protections of the health care law ,","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"and","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"by siphoning off healthy customers","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"( who were generally the only ones","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"who qualified for coverage under the old system ) ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"this would also skew the pool","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"covered on the exchanges ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"raising prices for everyone else .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"The White House has promised its own plan","depth":3},{"id":47,"text":"to help those","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"whose policies have been canceled","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"and who have not yet been able to sign up for new coverage .","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"There 's no word yet on what that plan might include ,","depth":3},{"id":51,"text":"but spokesman Jay Carney says","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"it will be announced sooner rather than later .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":105,"left":98,"right":104,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":81,"right":97,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},